snippet.title: Jack Move – Gameplay Trailer | Steam & Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Add Jack Move to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1099640/Jack_Move/

Jack Move is an RPG featuring gritty cyberpunk story telling, turn based battles and beautiful modern pixel art. Take on the role of Noa, a vigilante hacker who is thrust into a world of murder, kidnapping and dark research after her father goes missing.
